00:36:21,110 --> 00:36:22,450
I can send Gang out.

578
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:24,630
You'll go back to your Grand Paradise,

579
00:36:24,630 --> 00:36:26,630
and I'll continue
my construction business.

580
00:36:26,630 --> 00:36:27,630
What do you think?

581
00:36:28,470 --> 00:36:29,600
I see.

582
00:36:30,800 --> 00:36:32,260
You want me to

583
00:36:33,110 --> 00:36:35,480
sacrifice a piece and admit defeat, right?

584
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,510
Tianye.

585
00:36:37,550 --> 00:36:39,350
Even if a pawn crosses the river,

586
00:36:39,590 --> 00:36:41,190
it still can't become a rook.

587
00:36:42,190 --> 00:36:44,520
You don't know who'll have the last laugh.

588
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,260
Think about it.

589
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:48,840
No need.

590
00:36:49,190 --> 00:36:50,960
Wish you and Ms. Zhang

591
00:36:50,960 --> 00:36:52,490
a successful cooperation.

592
00:36:52,880 --> 00:36:53,670
In a few days,

593
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:55,650
I'll send you a big gift.

594
00:37:19,360 --> 00:37:19,910
Gang,

595
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:22,530
how's your injury?

596
00:37:24,030 --> 00:37:24,510
Muzhi.

597
00:37:25,510 --> 00:37:27,190
I'm fine. Everything's fine.

598
00:37:27,190 --> 00:37:28,070
Don't worry.

599
00:37:33,590 --> 00:37:35,120
Don't come over these days.

600
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:38,420
Wait for a while.

601
00:37:39,360 --> 00:37:41,220
The police might be watching you.

602
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:42,600
Just be careful.

603
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:45,120
Thanks, Young Mr. He.

604
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:55,560
Muzhi,

605
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:57,760
today...

606
00:37:59,750 --> 00:38:01,280
How's the weather outside?

607
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:03,610
The weather outside

608
00:38:04,710 --> 00:38:05,440
is not great.

609
00:38:07,630 --> 00:38:09,440
Liu Tianye called me.

610
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,050
He wants to talk.

611
00:38:11,710 --> 00:38:12,320
Muzhi.

612
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:14,650
It was my fault.

613
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:17,000
I messed it up.

614
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:19,640
I fell into their trap. I deserved this.

615
00:38:21,510 --> 00:38:21,960
Muzhi.

616
00:38:23,230 --> 00:38:24,540
Just leave me alone.

617
00:38:26,110 --> 00:38:27,970
Don't hold a grudge against them.

618
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:30,840
I don't want to drag you down anymore.

619
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:33,980
Now that they've reached out,

620
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:37,490
just talk to them.

621
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:38,740
Gang.

622
00:38:40,630 --> 00:38:42,230
I have nothing to say to them.

623
00:38:44,150 --> 00:38:45,650
I'm not holding a grudge

624
00:38:47,660 --> 00:38:49,510
but holding the stakes of our lives.
